Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.60,0:03:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们所在的诺拉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺拉核心部分的这段卫星主轴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与充当居住地的内壁完全分离
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.08,0:04:02.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此几乎没受到攻击的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:06.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让居民们到那里去避难
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若用各区域的运输升降机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疏散速度远胜过逃生艇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.87,0:04:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 诺拉整体正在发生扭曲瓦解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以需要歌姬号
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把歌姬号与轴心相连
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接牵引分离
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.10,0:04:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实 轴心有独立的维生系统
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 时间限制是5小时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.09,0:04:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不充裕但完全有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功与否全在大家的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对卫星主轴进行模拟计算
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:47.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令 请让我向歌姬号舰长戴安汇报情况
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将数据共享给歌姬号
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.88,0:04:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 敌人会坐视我们的行动不管吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:05:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 希望也许就在那台高达
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.22,0:05:05.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持秩序 保持秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,避难警报
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请大家按照指示前往农业区升降机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.53,0:05:14.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重复
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请大家按照指示前往农业区升降机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.06,0:05:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这货是精密机械
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.27,0:05:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要轻抬轻放！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.08,0:05:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凡格斯 要把AGE构筑系统运到哪里去？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.21,0:05:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,运到港口的联邦船上去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能晾在这儿被砸坏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.55,0:05:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AGE构筑系统和高达合在一起才叫AGE系统
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.83,0:05:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达就由你开到船上去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.43,0:05:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为防遇到战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带上光束枪和盾牌去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会马上去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:06:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要战斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.16,0:06:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米莉 迪克也在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太帅了 菲利特真的在开机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米莉 为什么来这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去升降机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.55,0:06:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特不去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.39,0:06:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得把高达送上船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道 菲利特也要一起上船？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.16,0:06:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 高达只有我能驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.67,0:06:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是真的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.06,0:06:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 艾米莉快去避难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈罗 你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是 你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 菲利特！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快走会被留下的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 人家那么担心他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.20,0:06:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过菲利特说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们赶紧去升降机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.95,0:06:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米莉 你去哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.01,0:06:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船那边 怎么能丢下菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:02.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？怎么都这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.63,0:07:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去 诺拉也完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.73,0:07:16.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和当时一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是人 没来得及避难吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.56,0:07:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着 马上来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为…为什么要逃？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再快点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.02,0:07:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里通向港口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.16,0:08:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么打开？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.81,0:08:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里怎么会有孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:16.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是军队专用的升降路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们想上港口的船
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.86,0:08:20.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别胡闹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平民快去农业区避难
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.66,0:08:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开闸门
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.33,0:08:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 果然被骂了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.13,0:08:35.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.65,0:08:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都到这里了怎么能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米莉？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米莉…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.99,0:08:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米莉 真是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.44,0:08:57.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布鲁扎司令说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:09:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是疯狂的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说要抽出卫星轴心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让歌姬号牵引住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算怎么办 冯罗德舰长？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.96,0:09:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然不会听他的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:12.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只要没有接到总司令部的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首要任务永远是保护舰船安全
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.81,0:09:19.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让歌姬号立即撤离危险的诺拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.08,0:09:22.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想对诺拉的人们见死不救？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还算是联邦军么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.20,0:09:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.28,0:09:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…古鲁迪克副司令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您来得真早啊 戴安·冯罗德舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来传达详细作战方案
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 你应该知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:47.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是联邦军总司令部的直辖部队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.89,0:09:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有必要听布鲁扎的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.88,0:09:51.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.83,0:09:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道就让开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:10:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古鲁迪克 你…你小子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.50,0:10:01.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要提高功率 照样可以要命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疯了吗 这是典型的叛国罪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犯罪受罚天经地义
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前提是 到时你我都还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:15.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.91,0:10:17.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.15,0:10:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是不是看到了不该看的东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.39,0:10:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令 只剩下我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.52,0:10:36.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去歌姬号上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.81,0:10:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我要留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.27,0:10:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分离卫星与轴心的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.06,0:10:44.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能在这里完成
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法远程操控
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.55,0:10:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.77,0:10:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道司令一开始就打算这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.19,0:10:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基地里有司令官专用的逃生通道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:11:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,专用的…逃生通道？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.46,0:11:02.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.56,0:11:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在歌姬号上协助大家避难
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救诺拉的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.69,0:11:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号托付给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,载着高达启程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.54,0:11:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…人类的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.58,0:11:19.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,专用的逃生通道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不存在的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亏我能说得那么若有其事
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.49,0:11:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是联邦军的新造战舰 歌姬号
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.47,0:11:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.85,0:11:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次看到实物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:11:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大好壮观
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轻放…轻放
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.32,0:12:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.17,0:12:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米莉？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.47,0:12:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没去卫星轴心避难吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.99,0:12:19.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来话长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们也上这艘船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.24,0:12:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 艾米莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.32,0:12:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可别到处乱跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.59,0:12:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.62,0:12:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰桥成员去哪儿了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴安舰长呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪 查不到乘员资料
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.03,0:12:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.03,0:12:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 现在是紧急事态
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:13:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠我们自己 让歌姬号出港
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员 开始准备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.27,0:13:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 军队的情报安保也不过如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可别怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.57,0:13:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号要为我所用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.08,0:13:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.01,0:13:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这就下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.84,0:13:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.36,0:13:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没受伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.99,0:13:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 那台高达是我造的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.71,0:14:00.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高…达？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.60,0:14:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达一定会救我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿能赶上船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.16,0:14:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一时不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.86,0:14:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 别放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.83,0:14:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫菲利特 你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚铃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚铃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚铃怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,UE的攻击好像还没结束
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.07,0:15:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚当斯 你不觉得这次敌人的攻击有古怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.73,0:15:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.53,0:15:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果敌人的目的是毁灭这座殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻击能源工厂就是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古鲁迪克副司令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.63,0:15:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 从现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.29,0:15:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这艘船的舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.78,0:15:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.86,0:15:40.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才 联邦军总司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨环基地发来指令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.56,0:15:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今天开始 我就任这艘歌姬号的舰长一职
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.22,0:15:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,操船成员与驾驶员登船了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:51.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号 紧急启航
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始连接卫星轴心的作业
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.44,0:16:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 高达还未搭载上船
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.83,0:16:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间了 让高达自主逃离诺拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.70,0:16:10.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号 出航准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.94,0:16:13.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命令舰外作业的乘员返回
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.42,0:16:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs52}歌姬号 出航准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs52\fad(0,400)}命令舰外作业的乘员返回
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么 高达还没上船呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认迁留装置分离
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.32,0:16:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维持周围警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:31.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入出港阶段一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.32,0:16:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我们掉进最底层的隔离区了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在这样 只能自己离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样直走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.59,0:17:04.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底右转
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.36,0:17:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认识出口？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.45,0:17:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 听我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.89,0:17:10.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别忘记剩余时间不多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员 开始连接卫星轴心的作业
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.84,0:17:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前进方向上发现疑似机动战士的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与袭击诺拉的属同类型
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:29.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时中止作业
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一级战斗配置
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.90,0:17:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 被堵住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.86,0:17:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.18,0:17:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4 3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.01,0:18:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入宇宙了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现高达
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.39,0:18:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来成功逃出了诺拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.38,0:18:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.47,0:18:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正与UE的机动战士型进入战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.47,0:18:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 好不容易逃出来又和敌人撞个正着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能干等着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:34.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正是AGE系统派用场的时候！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AGE系统？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.44,0:18:44.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的光束武器不管用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.52,0:18:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么打？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.19,0:18:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特 听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.83,0:18:48.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凡格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,临阵磨枪不快也光 使用AGE系统！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 有AGE系统
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.83,0:18:56.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人的解析数据呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.55,0:18:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数据的话 第一场战斗中收集到的足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.19,0:19:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上开始构筑新武器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.25,0:19:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 凡格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.15,0:19:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷 AGE系统到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.70,0:19:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是菲利特那小子造的好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.86,0:19:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,运用生物进化原理制造的机动战士构筑系统
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.87,0:19:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会根据战斗经历导出强化设计图
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,系统会自己造出强大的武器？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.30,0:19:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.22,0:19:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入高速成形阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AGE构筑系统 启动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.39,0:20:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞 完成了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.00,0:20:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么快？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.45,0:20:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 AGE构筑系统可以把铸块素材
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.14,0:20:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高速切割成部件并组装起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光束…步枪？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.53,0:20:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是烂大街的光束步枪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.33,0:20:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它可以让光束轨道呈螺旋状旋转
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.75,0:20:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贯穿力惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.45,0:20:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其名 多兹步枪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.56,0:20:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.76,0:21:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射高达部件 拿稳了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凡格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.71,0:21:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.90,0:21:26.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是…多兹步枪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.67,0:21:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.25,0:21:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.38,0:21:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达 击毁敌人机动战士型
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.45,0:21:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起 干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.19,0:22:00.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.41,0:22:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现新对象
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.35,0:22:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疑似机动战士的移动体接近
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.62,0:22:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.18,0:22:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.64,0:22:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的 和刚才不同
